29 SUMMARY
3300 This amendment includes fiscal year 2032-33 in the period of time for General Fund
3311 revenue to be transferred annually to a nonlapsing fund to be used to pay for retirement
3322 benefit improvements for retired state employees and teachers and their beneficiaries. It
3333 also provides that the amount transferred is equal to the difference between the amount of
3344 the payments made toward the unfunded actuarial liability from the General Fund in the
